title: PSP Crisis Core: Final Fantasy VII [cso]
description:
This is the prequal to Final Fantasy VII
This is a great game, and if you own a psp, you must play it.

Instructions:
Go into the root menu of your PSP
Open the ISO folder (if there isn't one, then make an ISO folder)
Copy and paste the file into the ISO folder (it is a CSO, but it doesn't matter)
Using latest Custom Firmware, you can go into your game foulder in the XMB menu 
Then select Crisis Core

(If you have a UMD in the PSP, you can go ahead and use that UMD ISO mode, but if there isn't a UMD in your PSP, change it to "SONY NP9660" it may help, it may do nothing, doesn't matter as long as you get the game to work)

Have fun!

Platform: Sony PSP
Genre: Fantasy RPG
Size: 1.06GB
